    "body": "- configure update to detect Fujitsu fortran compiler.\r\n- fix fox configure.\r\nfox's configure search -out and -o option to specify Fortran output file.\r\nFujitsu fortran accept -out option, but the output file cannot execute.\r\n- fix scalapack detection.\r\nWhen configue --scalapack=yes is specifies, configure append only -lscalapack option to linker.\r\nBut fujitsu SSL2 library on a64fx must use -lscalapacksve. So this PR set SCALAPACK_LIBS option.\r\n- fix intent and AND function usage.",
